text: Gilbert Le Bris (born March 3, 1949 in Concarneau) is a member of the National Assembly of France. He represents the Finistère department, and is a member of the Socialiste, radical, citoyen et divers gauche. ==References== Category:1949 births Category:Living people Category:People from Concarneau Category:Socialist Party (France) politicians Category:Deputies of the 12th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic Category:Deputies of the 13th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic Category:Deputies of the 14th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic
title: Gilbert Le Bris
